{
  "texts": [
    "This enables traceable and tamper-resistant documentation of sensory events, supporting source authentication and fraud prevention.",
    "In research and regulatory contexts, this integration also facilitates reproducibility by linking AI predictions to immutable data records.",
    "By combining the interpretive power of AI with the transparency of blockchain, such systems enhance trust in machine-sensed flavor and aroma assessments across food safety, quality assurance, and supply chain analytics.",
    "Virtual reality (VR) and augmented reality (AR) technologies provide immersive environments ideal for exploring and enhancing human sensory experiences, particularly in the realms of flavor and aroma (Bhavadharini et al. 2023).",
    "AI can significantly amplify these virtual sensory interactions by dynamically adjusting digital stimuli, offering highly customized or intensified perceptions in real-time."
  ]
}